text: So, @FedEx-waiting on expedited delivery by 8AM. Didn’t show& website didn’t have status. Package will be 90-120 minutes late. ? Is why do I have to wait 5 days to call # to request refund? Why can’t the CS rep I spoke to just now authorize it?
@MP_Billingsley Hello, this is Andrew. We apologize for this issue. Please DM @FedExHelp your name, delivery address, tracking & phone numbers and I would be happy to research this for you.
The length of time on hold with @FedEx is verging on #biblical. Package is 14 hours late and counting-they couldn’t locate it in Memphis. @FedExHelp

OK, @FedEx @FedExHelp spoke to three people to find out package is at Dulles. Trace rep has no idea when package will be delivered & tried to blame weather in Memphis when I was told that a plane broke. Rep copped an attitude and said nobody else could help.
